med drikking og kvinner.

594
00:34:53.651 --> 00:34:55.653
Robert likte å drikke whisky

595
00:34:55.736 --> 00:34:57.113
og elsket damer.

596
00:34:57.780 --> 00:35:01.033
Han elsket to ting, whisky og damer.

597
00:35:02.577 --> 00:35:05.204
Honeyboy var en annen bluesartist

598
00:35:05.288 --> 00:35:06.998
