629
00:36:34.585 --> 00:36:35.836
Han drakk den den dagen.

630
00:36:37.964 --> 00:36:41.092
Noen sier det var damen,
noen sier det var kjæresten,


631
00:36:41.175 --> 00:36:42.843
noen sier bartenderen.

632
00:36:42.927 --> 00:36:45.263
De visste bare at han var forgiftet.

633
00:36:46.305 --> 00:36:47.807
<i>Ifølge Honeyboy</i>

634
00:36:47.890 --> 00:36:49.767
<i>satt Robert fremoverlent,</i>

635
00:36:49.850 --> 00:36:52.812
<i>og de ville han skulle drikke mer</i>

636
00:36:52.895 --> 00:36:55.690
<i>for å spille videre,</i>
<i>men det kunne han ikke.</i>


637
00:36:56.899 --> 00:37:01.028
